s enough to convince the judges as to who would take the verdict.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both fighters\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"inactivity\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"that cagey\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"one real moment\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"quality\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"Staneva\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"the verdict\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh looked a bit more dynamic at the start of the second round, however, she soon ran out of ideas, and while both boxers scored with some clean shots, Staneva again with the more eye-catching efforts and won the round 4:1.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Walsh\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"ideas\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"both boxers\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"some clean shots\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"the more eye-catching efforts\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After losing the opening two rounds, Walsh really had to go after her opponent to attempt to cause a stoppage, however, Staneva reverted to type and boxed nicely off the back foot to select her shots and ease to the bell to ensure the unanimous victory.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening two rounds\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"Walsh\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"a stoppage\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"Staneva\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the back foot\", \"from